(306, 1, '2015-04-21 08:49:00', '2015-04-21 08:49:00', '<p>One of the key factors in our winning the Best Multilingual Website award in 2004 is our commitment to provide a top-class service to our customers, no matter where they are located. Our multilingual website and our 30 multilingual staff in the UK ensure that communication with our many international clients is never a problem.</p>\r\n', 'Best Multilingual Website 2004', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'best-multilingual-website-2004', '', '', '2015-04-21 19:45:12', '2015-04-21 19:45:12', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost//?post_type=cpt_award&#038;p=306', 2, 'cpt_award', '', 0),
(308, 1, '2015-04-21 08:50:43', '2015-04-21 08:50:43', '<p>We won the Queen’s Award for International Trade in 2008 after our expertise in supplying IBM ServicePacs and services to a world-wide clientele had led us to increasing our exports by 610% in just three years. David Moore, speaking on behalf of the Prime Minister’s advisory committee, praised us as an extemporary example of a company making a success of the EU market, proclaiming us as an example for other British companies to follow.</p>\r\n', 'Queens Award for International Trade 2008', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'queens-award-for-international-trade-2008', '', '', '2015-04-21 19:44:46', '2015-04-21 19:44:46', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost//?post_type=cpt_award&#038;p=308', 1, 'cpt_award', '', 0),
(309, 1, '2015-04-21 08:51:19', '2015-04-21 08:51:19', '<p>We are very proud to have been named as one of only 10 Yorkshire companies to win this year’s Queen’s Award for Enterprise in the category “International Trade”.</p>\r\n<p>The Queen’s Award is awarded only to the most outstanding companies or individuals in their respective specialised field and is divided into “International Trade”, “Innovation” and “Sustainable development”. In order to win the “International Trade” award, businesses must show a substantial increase in overseas growth and commercial success.</p>\r\n<p>With offices in the UK, Australia, Mauritius, throughout the African continent and now in the USA, Europlus Direct are globally present to supply 120 countries with IBM services. Having won the Queen’s Award previously in 2008, we are very pleased our continued effort to approach new markets and expand internationally has been recognised and rewarded with one of the UK’s most distinguished business awards.</p>\r\n', 'Queen’s Award for Enterprise 2013', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'queens-award-for-enterprise-2013', '', '', '2015-04-21 19:44:24', '2015-04-21 19:44:24', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost//?post_type=cpt_award&#038;p=309', 0, 'cpt_award', '', 0),
