(389, 1, '2015-04-23 13:04:16', '2015-04-23 13:04:16', '<p>As Financial Director of a global business, Rob manages the company’s cash flow, forecasting and budgeting to ensure that our finances run smoothly – in over 42 different currencies!</p>\r\n<p>Rob joined Europlus Direct in 2010 having worked previously in the translation industry at The Big Word and various companies within the advertising industry. Before that he completed a degree in Management and became ACMA qualified.</p>\r\n<p>Rob is a keen traveller, but when he’s not jet-setting, he enjoys many sports, especially football and more recently, golf. </p>', 'Rob Jobbins ACMA CGMA', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '250-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-04-23 13:04:16', '2015-04-23 13:04:16', '', 250, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost//uncategorised/250-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
