(403, 1, '2015-04-24 09:49:00', '2015-04-24 09:49:00', '<section class="section row two-box">\n<div class="section-content">\n<div class="row">\n<div class="small-12 large-6 columns blue-yellow-heading grey blue-sub-heads red-btns">\n<div class="nested-section-content section-content-inner">\n<h2 class="block-heading"><span class="line"><span class="block">IBM Software</span></span><span class="line"><span class="block secondary shift-right-55">Services</span></span></h2>\n<h4>Remote support keeps software performing</h4>\n<p>Don’t let software problems let your business down. With a Software Services Upgrade or Software Services Post Warranty, you’ll get remote technical support, which means there’s a virtual IT expert by your side whenever you need one.</p>\n<p>Keep your software–and your business–running smoothly with problem determination, problem resolution, performance and capacity management, preventative care and much more.</p>\n<p><strong>Software support features</strong></p>\n<ul class="bullet-list blue">\n<li>Remote technical support for System x and BladeCentre (1 or 3 year options)</li>\n<li>Support line for MS Windows or Linux on System x (1 or 3 year options)</li>\n<li>Support line for VMware (1 or 3 year options)</li>\n<li>Support line for Linux</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Want to know more about Europlus Direct’s IBM Software support? <a href="#">Read our FAQs</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Like more software advice? Call us on <a href="tel:">XXXX XXXXXXXX</a> or <a href="mailto:">email us now</a>.</strong></p>\n<footer class="text-right yellow-btns"><a class="read-more"><span class="inner">Webchat now?</span></a></footer>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="small-12 large-6 columns black yellow-blue-heading red-btns white-sub-heads">\n<div class="nested-section-content section-content-inner second">\n<h2 class="block-heading"><span class="line"><span class="block shift-right-55">IBM Multi-Manufacturer</span></span><span class="line"><span class="block secondary">Services</spa