(559, 1, '2015-04-25 17:22:04', '2015-04-25 17:22:04', '<h3>It doesn’t matter where you are based in the world or how many different locations you operate in, when it comes to worldwide IT support, Europlus Direct can help.</h3>\n<p>The worldwide hardware and software support that Europlus offers includes:</p>\n<ul class="bullet-list blue">\n<li>Hardware maintenance agreements</li>\n<li>Software maintenance agreements</li>\n<li>Hardware Service Pack In-warranty upgrades</li>\n<li>Software Service Pack In-warranty upgrades</li>\n<li>Hardware Service Pack Post-warranties</li>\n<li>Software Service Pack Post-warranties</li>\n<li>Hardware Multivendor Post-warranties</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Our Worldwide IT Services are ideal for distributors, business partners and companies individual consumers needing IBM or Lenovo services or indeed, those with hardware from other manufacturers.</p>', 'Multi-Country Maintenance', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '9-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-04-25 17:22:04', '2015-04-25 17:22:04', '', 9, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost//uncategorised/9-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
