(333, 1, '2015-04-21 16:11:15', '2015-04-21 16:11:15', '<p>What Michelle doesn’t do at Europlus Direct isn’t worth doing! When she’s not jetting off here there and everywhere, Michelle manages all departments and teams as well as the day-to-day running of EPD HQ.</p>\r\n<p>A self-confessed workaholic,<b><strong> </strong></b>Michelle redresses the balance with a<b><strong> </strong></b>love of socialising, learning how to ski, playing rounders and indulging in some serious retail therapy.</p>', 'Michelle Littlewood', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jim-hart', '', '', '2015-04-23 13:05:22', '2015-04-23 13:05:22', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost//?post_type=cpt_team&#038;p=333', 1, 'cpt_team', '', 0),
(334, 1, '2015-04-21 16:11:32', '2015-04-21 16:11:32', '<p>After<b><strong> </strong></b>spells working on client, Bet 365 at ICS and writing sport articles and a stint at an agency working on a campaign for an Italian ice cream company, Christian joined Europlus Direct in 2011.</p>\r\n<p>Originally from Sicily, Christian studied in Leeds, earning a degree in Business Management and a masters in Human Resources Management. In his spare time, he loves running, playing football and spending time with his dog – a fun-loving weimaraner called Eldon. <br /><br />Christian is also a film buff and loves reading books about the Italian Mafia.</p>', 'Christian Pullara', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jim-hart', '', '', '2015-04-23 13:08:25', '2015-04-23 13:08:25', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost//?post_type=cpt_team&#038;p=334', 6, 'cpt_team', '', 0),
(335, 1, '2015-04-21 16:11:50', '2015-04-21 16:11:50', '<p>German-born Marie learned English when she was 5 and spent a year in America. She joined Europlus Direct in 2011 and currently oversees all EPD Post-warranty activity across the globe.</p>\r\n<p>Before joining Europlus Direct, Marie enjoyed spells in Sales for Acorn Stairlifts and then providing solar panels for Evo Energy. </p>\r\n<p>A keen whiskey sampler, Marie enjoys cooking and reading.  Staff not only rely on Marie to keep things ship-shape at work, but also to help with the fun things in her role as a member of the EPD Social committee, as she organises social and charity events for the whole company.</p>', 'Marie Wollstadt', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'jim-hart', '', '', '2015-04-23 13:07:23', '2015-04-23 13:07:23', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost//?post_type=cpt_team&#038;p=335', 5, 'cpt_team', '', 0),
(336, 1, '2015-04-21 16:32:18', '2015-04-21 16:32:18', '<p>With all major European languages spoken in one office at our UK headquarters, we work in a diverse and inspiring environment – not least when we’re testing our taste buds with regular lunchtime buffets based on the latest country of choice. It’s busy too, and with monthly prizes such as holidays up for grabs for our best salespeople, it’s exciting with a competitive, but supportive edge.<br /><br />And if all that fun and excitement gets too much for staff, there’s always our stress-busting monthly massage days to fall back on–and enjoy!</p>\r\n<p>We’re a very ambitious, young company and with that, we greatly appreciate the efforts of all our colleagues who all benefit from clearly defined career paths and yearly salary increases, based on performance.</p>\r\n<p>Oh, and if any of our team is lucky enough to win a company holiday, our lovely modern offices are based right by the airport, which is handy for a quick getaway.</p>', 'Culture', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'culture', '', '', '2015-04-27 13:41:09', '2015-04-27 13:41:09', '', 47, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost//?page_id=336', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(337, 1, '2015-04-21 16:32:18', '2015-04-21 16:32:18', '<section class="section row  yellow above skewed  gutters overlap-bottom">\r\n<div class="section-inner">\r\n<div class="section-content">\r\n<h3 class="centered-text">Culture</h3>\r\n<p>With all major European languages spoken in one office at our UK headquarters, we work in a diverse and inspiring environment – not least when we’re testing our taste buds with regular lunchtime buffets based on the latest country of choice. It’s busy too, and with monthly prizes such as holidays up for grabs for our best salespeople, it’s exciting with a competitive, but supportive edge.</p>\r\n<p>And if all that fun and excitement gets too much for staff, there’s always our stress-busting monthly massage days to fall back on–and enjoy!</p>\r\n<p>We’re a very ambitious, young company and with that, we greatly appreciate the efforts of all our colleagues who all benefit from clearly defined career paths and yearly salary increases, based on performance.</p>\r\n<p>Oh, and if any of our team is lucky enough to win a company holiday, our lovely modern offices are based right by the airport, which is handy for a quick getaway.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="skewed-bg"> </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</section>', 'Culture', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '336-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-04-21 16:32:18', '2015-04-21 16:32:18', '', 336, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost//uncategorised/336-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(338, 1, '2015-04-21 10:21:57', '2015-04-21 10:21:57', '<p>We would like you to join our expanding sales team at Europlus Direct Ltd, based next to Leeds Bradford Airport. We have a new, bright office and an even better international team consisting of nationalities such as German, Italian, Spanish, French, Swedish, Dutch… and English. We have fun social events, an outside south facing dining area and even a masseur coming once a month. (What more could you ask for, right?)</p>\r\n<p>We are a global company with offices in the UK, Australia, USA &amp; Spain and we predict fantastic growth with annual turnover expected to double in the next 12 months. This is a fantastic opportunity to be a part of something special.</p>\r\n<p>Working on behalf of world renowned names in the IT industry our successful teams have won multiple awards including the Queens Award for International Trade (twice!), now in our 10th year in business, the company is expanding again into the USA.</p>\r\n<p>The successful candidate will be expected to develop new business, and nurture relationships with existing clients in France. This is an office-based role with potential opportunity to travel to France, attend external meetings with clients, suppliers and customers. </p>\r\n<p><strong>In order to be successful in this role you will have:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="bullet-list">\r\n<li>Fluent French and English</li>\r\n<li>Previous sales experience (face to face/telephone)</li>\r\n<li>Previous Customer Service experience</li>\r\n<li>Clear and confident telephone manner</li>\r\n<li>Strong written and oral communication skills</li>\r\n<li>Dynamic, outgoing attitude</li>\r\n<li>Excellent organisational skills</li>\r\n<li>The desire to hit targets and earn commission</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>The role:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="bullet-list">\r\n<li>Sales of IT services B2B into France (don’t worry, this isn’t a technical role and all training will be given!)</li>\r\n<li>Determining customer requirements and advising on product range, price and alternatives</li>\r\n<li>Assisting customers and providing excellent service</li>\r\n<li>Preparation of quotes, tenders, invoices etc.</li>\r\n<li>Management of customer database</li>\r\n<li>Sales Administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong> </strong></p>\r\n<p>To apply, please send your CV to <a href="mailto:anna.ceder@one-global.com">anna.ceder@one-global.com</a></p>\r\n<p>We look forward to hearing from you!</p>\r\n<p>Keywords: French Sales, French Account Manager, Sales Account Manager</p>', 'French Inside Sales Executive', 'We would like you to join our expanding sales team at Europlus Direct Ltd, based next to Leeds Bradford Airport. We have a new, bright office and an even better international team consisting of nationalities such as German, Italian, Spanish, French, Swedish, Dutch… and English. We have fun social events, an outside south facing dining area and even a masseur coming once a month. (What more could you ask for, right?)', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'french-inside-sales-executive', '', '', '2015-04-23 13:49:00', '2015-04-23 13:49:00', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost//careers/archive/french-inside-sales-executive-2/', 0, 'cpt_career', '', 0),
(339, 1, '2015-04-21 10:25:21', '2015-04-21 10:25:21', '<p><strong>Inside Sales Executive sought for global company with a great working environment and team! </strong></p>\r\n<p>We would like you to join our expanding sales team at Europlus Direct Ltd, based next to Leeds Bradford Airport. We have a great new office and an even better international team. We are a global company with offices in the UK, Australia, USA &amp; Spain and we predict fantastic growth with annual turnover expected to double in the next 12 months. This is a fantastic opportunity to be a part of something special.</p>\r\n<p>Working on behalf of world renowned names in the IT industry our successful teams have won multiple awards including the Queens Award for International Trade (twice!), now in our 10th year in business, the company is expanding again into the USA.</p>\r\n<p>The successful candidate will be expected to develop new business, and nurture relationships with existing clients. This is an office-based role with potential opportunity to travel to the US, attend external meetings with clients, suppliers and customers. </p>\r\n<p><strong>The role:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="bullet-list">\r\n<li>Sales of IT services B2B into the USA, this isn’t a technical role and all training will be given.</li>\r\n<li>Determining customer requirements and advising on product range, price and alternatives</li>\r\n<li>Assisting customers and providing excellent service</li>\r\n<li>Preparation of quotes, tenders, invoices etc.</li>\r\n<li>Management of customer database</li>\r\n<li>Sales Administration</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>In order to be successful in this role you will have:</strong></p>\r\n<ul class="bullet-list">\r\n<li>Previous sales experience (face to face/telephone)</li>\r\n<li>Previous Customer Service experience</li>\r\n<li>Clear and confident telephone manner</li>\r\n<li>Strong written and oral communication skills</li>\r\n<li>Dynamic, outgoing attitude</li>\r\n<li>Excellent organisational skills</li>\r\n<li>The desire to hit targets and earn</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>The shift pattern for this position is; Monday to Friday 2pm – 10pm</p>\r\n<p>If you would like to apply for this position then please email your CV to <a href="mailto:Sharon.craggs@one-global.com">Sharon.craggs@one-global.com</a>, or call me on 01138878367 to discuss further. I look forward to hearing from you.</p>\r\n', 'Inside Sales Executive – US market [de]', 'We would like you to join our expanding sales team at Europlus Direct Ltd, based next to Leeds Bradford Airport. We have a great new office and an even better international team. We are a global company with offices in the UK, Australia, USA & Spain and we predict fantastic growth with annual turnover expected to double in the next 12 months. This is a fantastic opportunity to be a part of something special.', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'inside-sales-executive-us-market', '', '', '2015-04-21 17:26:30', '2015-04-21 17:26:30', '', 0, 'http://europlusdirect.localhost//careers/archive/inside-sales-executive-us-market-2/', 0, 'cpt_career', '', 0),
